<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Aludie in talks, cautions shareholders.</title>
<headline>Aludie in talks, cautions shareholders.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Aluminium dye supplier Aludie Ltd said on Monday it was in talks and was undertaking a due diligence investigation which, if successfully concluded, could have an effect on its share price.</p>
<p>Shareholders were advised to exercise caution in their sharedealings until further notice.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27 11 482-1003</p>
